.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, malaysian, spanish
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, subway, train, trike
1. the malaysian is on the left of the spanish##1
2. the canadian is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
3. the person driving the trike is not the canadian##6
4. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
5. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
6. the spanish is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | canadian | malaysian | spanish     | american |
| Transport   | subway     | train    | quad-bike | trike    |

