.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, fonseca, tiparillo, davidoff
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, car, snowmobile
1. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
2. the davidoff-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person driving the car##5
3. the davidoff-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5
4. the fonseca-smoker is not the person driving the snowmobile##6
5. the person driving the bike is not the old-henry-smoker##6
6. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
7. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | old-henry        | davidoff | tiparillo | fonseca |
| Transport   | snowmobile | bike | boat     | car   |

