.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, boat, snowmobile, trike
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, colombian, indian, polish
1. the australian is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person driving the trike is not the colombian##6
3. the australian is on the far right##1
4. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
5. the person driving the snowmobile is the person driving the snowmobile##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the left of the australian##5
7. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the left of the person driving the airplane##5
8. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
9. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the left of the polish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | boat | snowmobile    | airplane  | trike   |
| Nationality   | indian  | polish | colombian | australian |

