.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, spy, time-travel, zombie
City: liverpool, boston, marseilles, prague
1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the person traveling to liverpool##3
2. the person traveling to marseilles is not the person watching spy movies##6
3. the person watching documentary movies is the person traveling to boston##1
4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
5. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left##1
6. the person watching spy movies is the person traveling to liverpool##1
7. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to liverpool##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | spy     | time-travel | documentary |
| Music-Genre   | marseilles | liverpool | prague      | boston         |

