.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
House: wooden, art-deco, cape-cod, farmhouse
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, journalist, photographer, social-worker
1. the coach is on the left of the journalist##1
2. the social-worker is somewhere to the left of the photographer##5
3. the social-worker is on the right of the journalist##1
4. the journalist is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
5. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the journalist##3
6. the coach is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
7. the farmhouse house is somewhere to the right of the cape-cod house##5
8. the art-deco house is not the social-worker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | art-deco  | wooden        | cape-cod      | farmhouse          |
| Job        | coach | journalist | social-worker | photographer |

