.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, hedgehog, rabbit
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, project-manager, journalist, scientist
1. the lawyer is not the owner of the ferret##6
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the scientist is the scientist##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the scientist##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is not the scientist##6
6. the project-manager is not the owner of the fish##6
7. the scientist is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the hedgehog is the lawyer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | hedgehog | ferret        | rabbit  | fish     |
| Sport   | lawyer     | scientist | project-manager | journalist |

