.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, pink, black, grey
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, indie, pop
1. the person who likes chestnut is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3
2. the fan electronic is somewhere to the left of the person who likes chestnut##5
3. the fan indie is not the person who likes black##6
4. the person who likes pink is between the fan pop and the person who likes black##2
5. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
6. the fan electronic is between the fan disco and the person who likes chestnut##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | black | pink    | chestnut | grey |
| Music-Genre   | disco         | electronic | pop   | indie     |

