2. the person eating banana is not the modern house##6
3. the person eating asparagus is the cottage house##1
4. the person eating lettuce is somewhere to the right of the modern house##5
5. the person eating asparagus is between the person eating banana and the cape-cod house##2
6. the person eating banana is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | pomegranate | banana      | asparagus | lettuce   |
| Movie-Genre   | modern     | wooden | cottage   | cape-cod |

