The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, water-polo, lacrosse, cricket
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not the person drinking water##6
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | water       | hot-chocolate | fanta     | lemonade     |
| Movie-Genre   | basketball | lacrosse       | cricket | water-polo |

