4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
5. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the subway is not the person watching action movies##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | fantasy | adventure | action | romance |
| Transport   | roller   | bike       | jet-ski    | subway     |

