.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, singing, skydiving, woodworking
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, helicopter, taxi, scooter
1. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5
2. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the helicopter##5
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the scooter is not the person who's hobby is board-games##6
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's hobby is singing##2
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
8. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the person driving the helicopter##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | singing | skydiving | board-games | woodworking |
| Pet     | taxi  | helicopter      | motorbike  | scooter       |

