The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, basketball, skateboarding, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
2. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
5. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##5
6. the person who's sport is basketball is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | almond-milk | iced-tea | water      | mirinda   |
| Transport   | tennis  | basketball   | skateboarding | parkour |

 